author: @Sea_witch_
text:
You can really catch a glimpse of their personalities in these photoshoots; Hyein really has an aura like a model, but very 90s top model aura, just fun, encouraging, fresh, yet mature and relaxed-joyful. Haerin's aura is just as it looks, peaceful indoor-backyard cat, classy and witty. Dani's aura is my favorite in many ways, I can tell she'll be the eccentric one in the group and her family, the rich auntie, the nature-sea lover, strong character and determined, but loving and open to understanding anyone, her beauty reflects just that, on top of the High-end fashion vibes. Minji is the closest to Korean fashion and classic faces in my opinion (although Hyein is too) both members remind me of city pop it girl singers from mid 90s to 2000s, Minji model version is serious, focused, does the job and goes home just as calm and focused, her maturity really shines through in these scenarios. If Minji is the leader, the main pillar that holds them together (they all are pillars) Hanni is the shield and moving force that moves them towards goals that they all share in common. Hanni has a very strong character aura too, sometimes Libra's vanity shows through her very strong! but she balances it out with her fun, carefree personality traits, the one closer to her mindset is definitely Dani, but they can clash because of it, always coming back to each other even so. 
These auras are HARD to find in kpop idols since 3rd gen, the industry knows it, such energies together AND such faces (all unique, heavenly, fresh, different, attract audiences all over the world) it isnt easy to find, not even in western music industry, where artists look more and more like each other. As a psychic myself, I would say more, but I leave it at that; I just found this video and realized how big of a future newjeans have ahead. All it took from me is to watch a few videos of them and I am taken, may they be protected AND TOGETHER always.
